_header: Man remember and have in mind
_description: On the need of foresight — five couplets

BLSl140.First Lines:
Ayen remember & have yn myndeOf vn ware wo þar comyth
                    behende…
BLSl140.Last Lines:
…Be wyse & ware loke well a bowtLett vertu enter &
                    vyce put owte
BLSl140.Note: Folio number reflects the most recent foliation.
